  "text": "It has been hypothesized that RAP lesions might respond more rapidly to intravitreal anti-VEGF therapies [CITATION_1] . This is in accordance with our results, considering that 81.5% of the total visual improvement and 85% of the total CMT reduction occurred during the first post-operative month, after one intravitreal injection of ranibizumab.",
